<dd><i>The Hungarian form of this <a href="/wiki/Personal_name" title="Personal name">personal name</a> is <b>Semmelweis Ignác Fülöp</b>. This article uses the <a href="/wiki/Personal_name#Name_order" title="Personal name">Western name order</a>.</i></dd>
</dl>
